{"tid":1254743,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊參選區議員","createTime":"2019-06-24T09:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T14:20:59.000Z","uid":258815,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"df889bc7f859edc72db4fca6d188a99948fba9e9","tid":1254743,"uid":258815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:06:39.000Z","msg":"呢排好多人推登記選民，<br />\n其實唔夠做。<br />\n因爲好多區冇競爭，俾啲民建聯、唔做野既或者選前先做野既連任。其實好唔抵！！<br />\n依加咁多人有知識、有能力又有心，但就唔敢出黎選<br />\n其實好嘥料。<br />\n各有各做可以考慮參選，一黎等排人冇咁易得米，二黎可以透過選舉動員，三黎如果成功可以喺制度內做易。"},{"pid":"84bf6b011e647260dc128f3758a69bf41a89b1be","tid":1254743,"uid":258815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:07:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbcf2753b30cd2481eb78de3a07b6d32cbfca704","tid":1254743,"uid":258815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:07:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cf0416954a38348cc9e5357b7d59f5b6e1227925","tid":1254743,"uid":258815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:08:16.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1d6d9ba6f5bd36580d101934306690d56169b781","tid":1254743,"uid":258815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:08:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"98c58045ed785a24da2529bfb5662002e866ad06","tid":1254743,"uid":258815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:10:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b614a97624b5644de8a2012a1e0f07267e325f58","tid":1254743,"uid":258815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:13:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"17f4f691a1b899be122601dabbca8a89d0318995","tid":1254743,"uid":258815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:15:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1217310b1fbdefc62d741faaf49f2be6e11c7154","tid":1254743,"uid":258815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:39:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6de5a7c4e4069cdb2e0272be7b6898f0c63b89b0","tid":1254743,"uid":218615,"like":0,"dis